 ('482', '212', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Apply Online for Current Job Openings\",\"slug\":\"apply-online-for-current-job-openings\",\"postDate\":1450482480,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"162\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Thank you for your interest in working for the City of Oakland!<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>For current City of Oakland or Port of Oakland employees, click here to view openings.<\\/li><li>For&nbsp;Port of Oakland jobs, click here to see available openings.<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 id=\\\"how-to-get-started-first-time-applicants\\\">How to Get Started: First-Time Applicants<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n  <li>Search for jobs that fit your skills and interests.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Save your search by setting up a job alert in a Job Interest Card.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>This will send you emails when new jobs open that fit your search criteria.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Click the \\u201cApply\\u201d link of a job you are interested in.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Create an account.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Select a username and password.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Click the \\u201cBuild Job Application\\u201d link to start your application.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Save your application as you complete sections.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>The NeoGov system will save your information every 15 minutes.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>You can save and use your application to apply for other job openings.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Online applications are stored on a secure site. Only authorized employees and hiring authorities have access to the information submitted.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 id=\\\"tips-for-completing-your-application\\\">Tips for Completing Your Application<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n  <li>Review the supplemental questions, if any are included.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>You may want to complete supplemental questions outside of the NeoGov system.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Other recommendations include:<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Gather information about your education and work experience.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Provide specific information in your answers such as dates, locations, data, and references.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Write responses in a word processing program such as Microsoft Word.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Copy and paste these responses into the NeoGov system.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Complete and submit your application before the closing date for consideration.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"5\":\"See all current job openings\",\"3\":\"Apply Online for Current Job Openings\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2015-12-19 00:13:18', '2015-12-19 00:13:18', '989ac9d4-673f-42ee-94ec-a39b971ca60f'),
