 ('1062', '632', '2', '512', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"512\",\"title\":\"Oakland Encourages Residents and Businesses to Prepare for El Ni\\u00f1o Storm Safety with \\u201cHow To\\u201d Videos \",\"slug\":\"oakland-encourages-residents-and-businesses-to-prepare-for-el-ni\\u00f1o-storm-safety-with-how-to-videos\",\"postDate\":1453075200,\"expiryDate\":1454198400,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p><strong>Oakland, CA<\\/strong> \\u2013 The City of Oakland encourages residents and businesses to&nbsp;prepare for El Ni\\u00f1o and strong winter storms. Three \\u201chow to\\u201d videos produced&nbsp;by the City provide quick, usable information about some specific, important&nbsp;steps to prepare for storms:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol><li>Building and using sandbags to protect against storm runoff and&nbsp;flooding<\\/li><li>Using plastic sheeting as an additional barrier<\\/li><li>Signing up for the City\\u2019s Adopt a Drain program to help prevent storm<\\/li><li>Drain blockages and flooding<\\/li><\\/ol><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/channel\\/UC4_la5PrP_f7f_PZPXo7D_w\\\">Watch and download videos on YouTube.<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We are asking&nbsp;the media to share and post these three public service announcements as part&nbsp;of your coverage of the winter weather.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>El Ni\\u00f1o is expected to bring winter storms significantly larger than normal, as&nbsp;well as the potential for flooding and other storm damage. Oaklanders need to&nbsp;work together to prepare and keep our city safe. It is vitally important that&nbsp;residents and businesses take steps to prepare for winter storms, and these&nbsp;videos show some effective steps.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/oakca1\\/groups\\/pwa\\/documents\\/pressrelease\\/oak056422.pdf\\\" target=\\\"true\\\">Download the PDF press release.<\\/a>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Medi